97
00:06:57,610 --> 00:07:01,170
Buying its servers
is the most direct solution.

98
00:07:02,490 --> 00:07:04,370
If you keep doing this,

99
00:07:04,490 --> 00:07:05,730
things will get bigger.

100
00:07:06,610 --> 00:07:07,730
