106
00:07:21,810 --> 00:07:25,290
With your current strength,
you're insignificant.

107
00:07:26,050 --> 00:07:27,050
It's hard to deal with it.

108
00:07:28,610 --> 00:07:29,290
How about this?

109
00:07:29,610 --> 00:07:30,610
You leave it to me.

110
00:07:30,730 --> 00:07:31,490
Wait.

111
00:07:31,610 --> 00:07:33,050
Can you give me some more time?

112
00:07:33,050 --> 00:07:34,050
Yes, I can.

113
00:07:34,050 --> 00:07:35,810
That's why I asked you out.

114
00:07:36,610 --> 00:07:37,490
You should know

115
00:07:38,050 --> 00:07:39,290
