122
00:08:01,050 --> 00:08:02,170
Here you go.

123
00:08:03,170 --> 00:08:04,410
Thank you.

124
00:08:07,330 --> 00:08:07,890
Come on.

125
00:08:08,850 --> 00:08:09,410
I can open mine.

126
00:08:22,170 --> 00:08:22,970
Actually,

127
00:08:24,970 --> 00:08:26,810
