128
00:08:27,610 --> 00:08:29,290
If we find the person behind this,

129
00:08:30,170 --> 00:08:31,290
it will be beneficial for me,

130
00:08:32,050 --> 00:08:32,810
this industry,

131
00:08:33,170 --> 00:08:36,050
and even Lansheng.

132
00:08:37,930 --> 00:08:40,490
Now it's just a temporary sacrifice
of Fragment Time Boyfriend.

133
00:08:41,530 --> 00:08:44,610
I will make this sacrifice worthwhile.

134
00:08:52,050 --> 00:08:52,610
Okay.

135
00:08:53,610 --> 00:08:54,930
Since you've said so,

136
00:08:55,530 --> 00:08:56,970
I respect your decision.

137
00:08:57,850 --> 00:08:59,730
Actually, I just wanted to remind you.

138
00:09:00,170 --> 00:09:01,530
Lansheng is running out of patience.

139
00:09:02,290 --> 00:09:03,850
Whatever decision you want to make,

140
00:09:04,410 --> 00:09:05,530
act as fast as you can.

141
00:09:07,610 --> 00:09:09,730
I can't favor you at work.

142
00:09:10,610 --> 00:09:12,610
In private, I can only advise you.

143
00:09:14,610 --> 00:09:16,730
But if you need the investment company
to do anything,

144
00:09:17,170 --> 00:09:19,610
