243
00:14:45,970 --> 00:14:47,850
We did it.

244
00:14:47,850 --> 00:14:49,290
Our efforts were not in vain.

245
00:14:49,970 --> 00:14:50,850
I told you we could do it.

246
00:14:50,850 --> 00:14:51,290
Right?

247
00:14:51,730 --> 00:14:52,730
Yes, we can.

248
00:14:52,850 --> 00:14:54,930
Let's celebrate tonight.

249
00:14:54,930 --> 00:14:55,970
Of course.

250
00:14:55,970 --> 00:14:56,610
Where to go?

251
00:14:56,730 --> 00:14:57,170
Let's go.

252
00:14:57,530 --> 00:14:58,530
I think

253
00:14:58,970 --> 00:15:00,210
I should tell you.

254
00:15:00,730 --> 00:15:02,810
Fragment Time Boyfriend was hacked.

255
00:15:02,810 --> 00:15:04,410
To protect the players' rights,

256
00:15:04,410 --> 00:15:06,610
An Ran stood up to Lansheng
and got suspended.

257
00:15:13,090 --> 00:15:14,930
Bluebird was nominated
in an animation competition,

258
00:15:14,930 --> 00:15:16,570
for outstanding work.

259
00:15:16,570 --> 00:15:18,930
